reporting-org.narrative: United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs

description.narrative: Le BCAH coordonne les interventions d’urgence au niveau mondial pour sauver des vies et protéger les populations en cas de crise humanitaire. Nous plaidons pour une action humanitaire efficace et raisonnée, par tous et pour tous

The Ebola Response is highly complex. It requires the continuous effort by hundreds of different kinds of organizations and thousands of people to implement it quickly, effectively and efficiently. Countries large and small have stepped up to provide doctors, mobile clinics, and funding. These efforts show the immense value of international cooperation. The response efforts need to be maintained in Guinea and Sierra Leone and we are committed to assisting these countries reach and stay at zero cases.
